{"tid":2129600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武肺免費測試 Circle project係支那公司","createTime":"2020-07-28T16:58:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T04:22:25.000Z","uid":137078,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a77a0a14eeb645eab88080fddfcf236c3ad9873d","tid":2129600,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T16:58:19.000Z","msg":"Source :link<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林鄭公佈的最新防疫措施還有這麼一條：<br />\n<br />\n- 政府不排除向私人化驗所購買檢測服務<br />\n<br />\n網友跟我分享說家人在賽馬會領了基因測試盒，上面寫着「圓基因」出品：<br />\n<br />\n//22間指定普通科門診診所今日起免費派發深喉唾液樣本瓶。<br />\n<br />\n早上七時前，鑽石山東九龍普通科門診外排隊領取樣本瓶的人龍，沿斧山道延伸數十米，診所有110個樣本瓶名額。<br />\n<br />\n有職員向較後位置的市民解釋每日名額有限，呼籲他們翌日再領取樣本瓶。<br />\n<br />\n診所七時半起，有穿着全套保護衣的人員向市民派發樣本瓶及採集指引，排頭位的市民清晨五時許已經到場，有人指住所附近有人確診，希望取得樣本瓶。//<br />\n<br />\n關於圓基因的背景，我已寫過了，在被利用恐慌而想去免費領取之前，請大家和家人好好參詳一下：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2880103158706470&amp;id=972393926144079\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2880103158706470%26id%3D972393926144079&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaDz%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=d484fce5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2880103158706470&amp;id=972393926144079</a><br />\n<br />\n//未知這種背景的一般市民，見到GEM賣廣告推銷「圓基因」30秒測測你的健康隱患，很可能會心動交出自己的DNA，當做一份體檢報告；但你的基因樣本到頭來如何被集檔、儲存、標記甚或轉售，你又有沒有想過？你又是否知道搞Circle的這間初創Prenetics，有阿里巴巴等陸企泵水四億支持？<br />\n<br />\n香港01報道：「Prenetics行政總裁楊聖武指，期望透過平台Circle，令大眾認識基因與保健關係，使基因測試在香港更普及。」<br />\n<br />\n在香港更普及？建立香港人基因數據庫？//<br />\n<br />\n（分享類似的東西時，記得把數字和QR打格）<br />\n<br />\n作者<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/972393926144079/posts/3385170211533093/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F972393926144079%2Fposts%2F3385170211533093%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=jpV%2F2%2Bss%2F2Wq3uOsKpdaDz%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=de26e4a0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/972393926144079/posts/3385170211533093/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span class=\"red\">Circle= Prenetics = 阿里巴巴泵水=支那嘢嚟<br />\n免費野更貴<br />\n<br />\np係港共政府資助搞港版健康碼嘅三間公司之一<br />\n仲有一單係測試無醫生轉介就做，違晒規<br />\n不過有港共照 唔會有事<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"547df7059d720184d9328b0b931b8963bea643ad","tid":2129600,"uid":137078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T16:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VBJUpnA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVBJUpnA.jpg&h=03c42339&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖 作者fb"},{"pid":"f1b8fa6033fdf8be9f33a6e73111921b98458abb","tid":2129600,"uid":12929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T16:59:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eae04375af1ca47de5fdd80c134fc783b9b37942","tid":2129600,"uid":128558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T18:36:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69f564fd6045d576c54fe9a173538bb5d7ec8b9b","tid":2129600,"uid":137078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eae04375af1ca47de5fdd80c134fc783b9b37942","tid":2129600,"uid":128558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T18:36:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T20:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f17ddc0dc54b9a1f52310e7c86183690ebb0c5","tid":2129600,"uid":74214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T20:40:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e8ff495fe27e704baf450740420c77b84062ab","tid":2129600,"uid":223868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T20:55:47.000Z","msg":"返